---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContentPage from '../components/ContentPage.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Responsible Use | Fight Prophet"
  description="Responsible-use guidance for Fight Prophet predictions, rankings, and MMA analytics. Educational information only, not betting or financial advice."
>
  <ContentPage
    eyebrow="Responsible Use"
    title="Responsible Use"
    intro="Fight Prophet is an educational analytics site. Predictions and rankings are estimates built from historical data, not instructions to bet, invest, or take financial risk."
    updated="May 17, 2026"
  >
    <section>
      <h2>Educational Use Only</h2>
      <p>
        Fight Prophet can help readers understand probability, calibration, ranking movement,
        and model uncertainty. It cannot know the future, account for every private factor,
        or remove risk from a fight outcome.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Do Not Treat Outputs As Advice</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Do not treat a model edge as a guaranteed result.</li>
        <li>Do not risk money you cannot afford to lose.</li>
        <li>Do not use the site where betting is illegal or restricted.</li>
        <li>Do not ignore local age limits, tax obligations, or gambling rules.</li>
        <li>Do not chase losses or increase risk because a model was wrong.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>When To Step Away</h2>
      <p>
        If sports betting stops feeling optional, creates stress, affects relationships, or
        leads to chasing losses, pause and seek support from qualified local resources. A
        prediction model should never pressure a reader into action.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="fp-content-note">
      <h2>Site Position</h2>
      <p>
        Fight Prophet does not sell guaranteed picks, does not promise winnings, and does
        not provide financial advice. Model outputs can be wrong even when the historical
        signal looks strong.
      </p>
    </section>
  </ContentPage>
</BaseLayout>
